      "comment": "MAJOR LOSE (6) comes off an average performance last start when sixth at this track over 390m behind Moraine Casma (23.24) in a T3 Grade 7. Better than the latest run and deserves another chance. SALLY SHINE (8) has been beaten for early speed lately, last time finishing fifth (22.79) in a Bottom Up - Restricted Win at Warrnambool. Goes very well here finding the frame in each of three starts. Must be included in calculations. MACK IN BOOTS (5) was in the minors two back (22.56) at this track but ran below best last time at Healesville, finishing 6th. Form from his last run is proving strong. Shapes as one to consider. HOLLY BLUE GIRL (2) can fill a top-three spot.",
